The,WSO,API,Cloud,API,simplifies,the,sharing,of,enterprise,capabilities,in,the,cloud,environment,Its,architecture,features,the,publisher,storage,gateway,and,key,manager,functionalities,The,publisher,functionality,supports,the,management,of,the,API,s,lifecycle,right,from,publishing,to,documentation,sharing,API,key,provisioning,and,user,feedback,collection,The,storage,functionality,allows,users,to,access,deploy,and,exploit,the,different,functional,properties,of,APIs,while,the,gateway,functionality,operates,as,a,scalable,portal,for,routing,the,traffic,of,API,calls,As,for,the,key,manager,functionality,it,is,the,security,portal,for,authenticating,and,validating,the,API,s,access,credentials,The,RESTful,API,requires,token,authentication,and,uses,the,HTTP,method,to,transmit,requests